      </div>
      <p>
        The <span class='bookTitle'>Diaolongbei</span> <a href='/word_detail.php?id=25506' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '雕龍碑 Diāolóngbēi', 'Diaolongbei')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">雕龙碑</a> site is located about 25 km northeast of the city of Zaoyang, Hubei.
        The site was discovered in 1957 and has plentiful late Neolithic artifacts, including dwellings, cellars, tombs, 
        eating utensils, and tools.
        The picture below shows a painted pottery container from the <span class='bookTitle'>Diaolongbei</span> site.
      </p>
      <div class="picture">
